    q: "What does CADR mean?",
    a: "CADR stands for Clean Air Delivery Rate. It measures the volume of clean air an air purifier produces per minute, typically broken down into scores for dust, pollen, and smoke. A higher CADR means the purifier can clean the air faster and handle a larger room."
