---

<SiteLayout
  site="fixitwithducttape"
  title="Best Air Purifiers 2026"
  description="Compare top air purifiers from Dyson, Coway, Levoit, Blueair, and more based on CADR, room size, filter type, noise, energy, and smart features."
  canonical="https://fixitwithducttape.photonbuilder.com/best-air-purifiers"
  schema={schema}
>
  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Best Air Purifiers 2026</h1>
      <p>Breathe easier with our top picks. We compared the leading air purifiers to find the best options for allergies, pets, smoke, and large rooms.</p>
    </div>

    <section class="content-section">
      <p>Indoor air can often be more polluted than outdoor air. An effective air purifier can significantly improve your home environment by removing allergens, dust, smoke, and odors. We've evaluated the top models on the market, analyzing their filtration technology, clean air delivery rate (CADR), room coverage, and ongoing costs to help you find the perfect match for your needs.</p>

      <h2>Category Winners</h2>
      <div class="winners-grid">
        {categoryWinners.map(w => (
          <div class="winner-card">
            <span class="winner-label">{w.category}</span>
            <strong>{w.pick}</strong>
            <span class="winner-reason">{w.reason}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <h2>Comparison Table</h2>
      <p>Click any column header to sort the data. Prices and filter costs are estimated standard retail pricing.</p>
      <div class="table-wrapper">
        <table id="comparison-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th data-sort="string">Model</th>
              <th data-sort="string">Filter Type</th>
              <th data-sort="number">CADR</th>
              <th data-sort="number">Room Size</th>
              <th data-sort="number">Noise</th>
              <th data-sort="number">Energy</th>
              <th data-sort="number">Filter Cost</th>
              <th data-sort="number">Price</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {purifiers.map(p => (
              <tr>
                <td><strong>{p.name}</strong></td>
                <td>{p.type}</td>
                <td data-value={p.cadr}>{p.cadr}</td>
                <td data-value={p.roomSize}>{p.roomSizeStr}</td>
                <td data-value={p.noiseLevelNum}>{p.noiseLevel}</td>
                <td data-value={p.energyNum}>{p.energyConsumption}</td>
                <td data-value={p.filterReplacementCost}>{p.filterReplacementStr}</td>
                <td data-value={p.price}>{p.priceStr}</td>
              </tr>
            ))}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <h2>Detailed Reviews</h2>

      {purifiers.map((p, i) => (
        <div class="review-card">
          <div class="review-header">
            <div>
              <span class="review-rank">#{i + 1}</span>
              <h3>{p.name}</h3>
              {p.badge && <span class="badge">{p.badge}</span>}
            </div>
            <span class="review-price">{p.priceStr}</span>
          </div>

          <p class="review-summary">{p.summary}</p>

          <div class="specs-grid">
            <div class="spec"><span class="spec-label">Filter Type</span><span class="spec-value">{p.type}</span></div>
            <div class="spec"><span class="spec-label">CADR</span><span class="spec-value">{p.cadr}</span></div>
            <div class="spec"><span class="spec-label">Room Size</span><span class="spec-value">{p.roomSizeStr}</span></div>
            <div class="spec"><span class="spec-label">Noise Level</span><span class="spec-value">{p.noiseLevel}</span></div>
            <div class="spec"><span class="spec-label">Energy</span><span class="spec-value">{p.energyConsumption}</span></div>
            <div class="spec"><span class="spec-label">Filter Cost</span><span class="spec-value">{p.filterReplacementStr}</span></div>
            <div class="spec"><span class="spec-label">Smart Features</span><span class="spec-value">{p.smartFeatures}</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="pros-cons">
            <div class="pros">
              <h4>Pros</h4>
              <ul>{p.pros.map(pro => <li>{pro}</li>)}</ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cons">
              <h4>Cons</h4>
              <ul>{p.cons.map(con => <li>{con}</li>)}</ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      {faqs.map(f => (
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>{f.q}</h3>
          <p>{f.a}</p>
        </div>
      ))}

    </section>
  </div>

  <script is:inline>
    (function() {
      const table = document.getElementById('comparison-table');
      if (!table) return;
      const headers = table.querySelectorAll('th');
      let currentSort = { col: -1, asc: true };

      headers.forEach((th, index) => {
        th.style.cursor = 'pointer';
        th.addEventListener('click', () => {
          const sortType = th.dataset.sort;
          const asc = currentSort.col === index ? !currentSort.asc : true;
          currentSort = { col: index, asc };

          headers.forEach(h => h.classList.remove('sort-asc', 'sort-desc'));
          th.classList.add(asc ? 'sort-asc' : 'sort-desc');

          const tbody = table.querySelector('tbody');
          const rows = Array.from(tbody.querySelectorAll('tr'));

          rows.sort((a, b) => {
            const cellA = a.children[index];
            const cellB = b.children[index];
            let valA, valB;

            if (sortType === 'number') {
              valA = parseFloat(cellA.dataset.value || cellA.textContent.replace(/[^0-9.\-]/g, ''));
              valB = parseFloat(cellB.dataset.value || cellB.textContent.replace(/[^0-9.\-]/g, ''));
              return asc ? valA - valB : valB - valA;
            } else {
              valA = cellA.textContent.trim().toLowerCase();
              valB = cellB.textContent.trim().toLowerCase();
              return asc ? valA.localeCompare(valB) : valB.localeCompare(valA);
            }
          });

          rows.forEach(row => tbody.appendChild(row));
        });
      });
    })();
  </script>

  <style is:inline>
    .page-content { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 3rem 0 2rem; }
